NAME
    SVN::Simple::Hook - Simple Moose-based framework for Subversion hooks

VERSION
    version 0.110070

SYNOPSIS
        package MyHook;
    
        use Moose;
        extends 'MooseX::App::Cmd::Command';
        with 'SVN::Simple::Hook';
    
        1;

DESCRIPTION
ATTRIBUTES
  repos_path
    Directory containing the Subversion repository.

AUTHOR
    Mark Gardner <mjgardner@cpan.org>

